headline.main: CHAIM WEIZMANN OF ISRAEL IS DEAD; Nation's First Executive, 77, a Leader Among Founders as Zionist -- Noted Chemist

snippet: TEL AVIV, Israel, Sunday, Nov. 9 -- President Chaim Weizmann of Israel died at 6:30 this morning in his home in Rehovot, near here, after a long illness. He would have been 78 years old on Nov. 27.
